You find yourself in an enchanted labyrinth of abandoned premises, and the only way to survive is to collect all the notes and find a way to the exit, avoiding a meeting with a dangerous ghost.

Explore the gloomy corridors of abandoned premises, full of dangers and secrets. Each step can lead to new tricks or unexpected finds. Unravel the history of this cursed place, collecting notes left by previous inhabitants.

The atmosphere of the game is filled with tension and fear. Discover dark secrets and show your courage to survive this terrible test. Will you be able to escape from the ghost and unravel the secrets of the abandoned labyrinth?

GAME FEATURES:
• Exciting and dangerous atmosphere;
• An abandoned labyrinth with many secrets;
• Tense and gloomy soundtrack;
